trans-unit.target: O método de retorno de chamada.

trans-unit.source: References the method to call when retrieving field data from a provider.
trans-unit.target: Faz referência ao método a ser chamado ao recuperar dados do campo de um provedor.

trans-unit.source: When a Web Parts control provides data through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartField> interface, the consumer or transformer must retrieve and process the field data from the provider.
trans-unit.target: Quando um controle de Web Parts fornece dados por meio de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartField> interface, o consumidor ou transformador deve recuperar e processar os dados do campo do provedor.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.FieldCallback> delegate represents the method to call for processing the provider data.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.FieldCallback> delegate representa o método a ser chamado para processar os dados do provedor.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartField.GetFieldValue%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method contains a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.FieldCallback> delegate parameter.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartField.GetFieldValue%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> método contém um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.FieldCallback> delegar o parâmetro.
